{
  "stem": "15396.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were just following orders.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was the, I suppose-- well, yes, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only time, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had some things that we had to-- and he was using toothpaste and things, putting in that, and you know good and well that's not going to work very long.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe once or twice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also a refugee who was thinking that, well, he'd get rid of it in a hurry, and some of our messages might not get through that way.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had a series of messages that had-- at the very end there-- that had to get through, and that's what they did.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What they did is type them on very thin paper, you know, and rolled it up very tight, and put it in--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Telling who the people were, and where they were, and how to contact them, and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they had to do-- all to do with the refugees, what was needed for them and who they were, because-- and the sort of things that, as Fry said in his book, when I was arrested in Spain, he said it produced panic in them-- panic in them because they knew how sensitive this stuff was.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But thanks to that-- those pornographic drawings, and thanks to that chasing, carrying the luggage for those people, we didn't get caught.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I say, adrenaline is a great--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Lisbon, eventually.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Spain, and then all through Spain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, they had to have these Spanish-- and there was a man I got to know later.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Name is Carlos [? de Rafael. ?] He had been in the consulate there, and later on I ran into him in Spain when I was filming there.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
